Trvais Scott Tracks

By: Adrian Marquez

Travis Scott is an American rapper, singer, songwriter, and record producer known for his innovative sound and energetic performances. Born Jacques Webster on April 30, 1991, in Houston, Texas, he rose to fame with his mixtapes, particularly "Rodeo" in 2015, which showcased his unique blend of hip-hop, trap, and psychedelic elements. Scott is also recognized for his collaborations with major artists and his partnership with brands like Nike and McDonald's. His album "Astroworld" (2018) solidified his status in the music industry, featuring hits like "Sicko Mode." Beyond music, Scott is known for his artistic vision and immersive live shows, making him a prominent figure in contemporary culture
